data.description: HIDDEN GEM nestled in the heart of Cape Coral! Imagine life on a tranquil cul-de-sac on a quarter acre of prime property! Housed in 1800 sq ft of spacious living, this single-family home contains 3 beds plus a den and 2 baths and is designed perfectly for family living! Guests will be greeted by a stunning landscaped entrance and paved sitting area where you can savor your morning coffee. Inside, the wood laminate flooring enhances the beauty of a large, open living area designed as a split floor plan to maximize space and privacy. Cook and dine in style in your semi-private kitchen that features both a separate dining area and breakfast bar plus a mini-fridge for your favorite beverages. Indulgent master suite with a separate rain shower and the essential walk-in closet. Enjoy the sunshine inside or out in the enclosed lanai or out on the extended open patio overlooking a spacious yard. PLUS Solar panels are your ticket to eco-friendly and economical living. Located near Pine Island Road and neighborhood favorite Farmer Joe’s, plus gyms, upscale restaurants, and local shops. This sunny Cape Coral lifestyle is waiting for you. Make 1432 SW Terrace your forever home today!
